import React from "react"; import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css'; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import Typewriter from "typewriter-effect"; function Birthday(){ const navigate = useNavigate(); return <>

{ typewriter.typeString('Happy Birthday Ronak ') .callFunction(() => { console.log('String typed out!'); }) .pauseFor(10000) .deleteAll() .callFunction(() => { console.log('All strings were deleted'); }) .start(); }} />

} export default Birthday;
